videos.headline: Missouri's Lock throws 36th TD pass of the season
videos.description: Drew Lock pass finds Albert Okwuegbunam in the corner of the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown to put Missouri ahead early in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Missouri's Sparks gives Tigers short field after interception
videos.description: Adam Sparks telegraphs Kyle Shurmur's pass and returns it 7 yards to give Missouri good field position.

videos.headline: Missouri's Moore's 71-yard reception puts Tigers in the red zone
videos.description: Drew Lock throws a dime to J'Mon Moore for a 71-yard pass to Vanderbilt's 12-yard line to set up the Tigers.

videos.headline: Missouri's Rountree III just crosses the plane for TD run.
videos.description: Drew Lock pitches it to Larry Rountree III, who runs to the outside for a 12-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Lee widens Tigers' lead with pick-6
videos.description: Brandon Lee intercepts Kyle Shurmur's pass and returns it 42 yard for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Missouri's Floyd tip toes sideline for 30-yard TD
videos.description: Drew Lock throws a strike to Richaud Floyd as the defender falls for a 30-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Missouri's Floyd breaks free for 74-yard punt return
videos.description: Richaud Floyd runs down the sidelines and sprints to the end zone for a 74-yard punt return.

videos.headline: Odom says D-line has been able to get pressure on Vanderbilt
videos.description: Missouri's head coach Barry Odom says the Tigers' offense is "struggling at a couple things" despite 35 first-half points.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Webb leaps into the end zone for TD
videos.description: Ralph Webb jumps into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown to get Vanderbilt into the end zone for the first time all game.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt closes gap with TD
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur finds Caleb Scott wide open in the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Missouri's Okwuegbunam beats defenders for 57-yard TD
videos.description: Drew Lock throws a strike to Albert Okwuegbunam over the middle fora 57-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Missouri picks off Shurmur
videos.description: Terry Beckner Jr. perfectly times Kyle Shurmur's pass , intercepts it and returns it for 49 yards.

videos.headline: Missouri bowl eligible after 45-17 win over Vanderbilt
videos.description: Andre Ware says it would've been hard for Vanderbilt to beat Missouri after the Tigers dominated in all three phases of the game.
